身为[[Windows_2000|Windows 2000]]技术的继任者，'''Windows XP'''在引入诸多新功能的同时，亦移除诸多旧功能。下面将介绍XP系统移除的功能。
{{Windows XP}}

== 内核 ==
* 移除不安全设备对话框被删除<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.msdn.com/b/oldnewthing/archive/2003/12/16/43890.aspx|title=The unsafe device removal dialog|author=Raymond Chen|date=2003-12-16|work=The Old New Thing - MSDN Blogs|accessdate=2013-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130308032608/http://blogs.msdn.com/b/oldnewthing/archive/2003/12/16/43890.aspx|archive-date=2013-03-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* [[Windows资源管理器|Windows资源管理器]]中不可以查看小图标<ref>{{cite web|url=http://winsupersite.com/article/windows-7/windows-7-feature-focus-windows-explorer|title=Windows 7 Feature Focus: Windows Explorer|author=Paul Thurrott|date=2010-10-06|work=Paul Thurrott's SuperSite for Windows|accessdate=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130107055320/http://winsupersite.com/article/windows-7/windows-7-feature-focus-windows-explorer|archive-date=2013-01-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
* “桌面图标排列”命令不可用，由“对齐到网格”命令取代<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/293478|title=Line Up Icons Command Is Missing on Windows XP Desktop|author=Microsoft|date=2006-01-27|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071214094553/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/293478|archive-date=2007-12-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，该切换简化桌面图标位置调整的操作，无需[[单击|单击]]确定图标的位置<ref name="karp2005">{{cite book|title=Windows XP in a Nutshell|first1=David A.|last1=Karp|first2=Tim|last2=O'Reilly|first3=Troy|last3=Mott|publisher=O'Reilly Media, Inc.|location=Sebastopol, CA|year=2005|isbn=0596009003|accessdate=2012-11-07|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=5_UoYcmkvncC&lpg=PP1&pg=PP1#v=onepage&q&f=false|edition=2nd|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407094829/http://books.google.ca/books?id=5_UoYcmkvncC&lpg=PP1&pg=PP1#v=onepage&q&f=false|archive-date=2014-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{rp|47}}。
* 任务栏隐藏了“最小化所有窗口”命令<ref name="karp2005" />{{rp|76}}，以“显示桌面”取代，但该命令仍被保留，实际功能仅是暂时隐藏窗口而不是减少窗口数量，该命令仍能透过键盘热键组合{{key press|Win}}+{{key press|M}}激活。
* 鉴于图标的色彩丰富，“显示”属性中“使用所有可用的颜色显示图标”选项删除<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/282432|title="Show icons using all possible colors" Option Is Not Available|author=Microsoft|date=2006-01-15|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090112125824/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/282432|archive-date=2009-01-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* “显示”属性“设置”选项卡中“[[视频图形阵列|视频图形阵列]][[显示分辨率|显示分辨率]]”和“8位[[颜色深度|颜色深度]]选项”被移除，可以利用高级选项调用，但这种功能已不支持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/286906|title=Cannot Change Display Setting to 640 X 480 or 256 Color|author=Microsoft|date=2006-01-15|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2013-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070219235217/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/286906|archive-date=2007-02-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* 文件夹“Web试图”默认禁用，可透过编辑注册表恢复。此外，“定制文件夹向导”被删除<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/819028|title=Windows Explorer no longer displays Web view templates or HTML customizations (using Folder.htt)|author=Microsoft|date=2007-10-26|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20041020044404/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/819028|archive-date=2004-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于Web视图的删除，打开驱动器时显示磁盘空间的[[饼图|饼图]]不能显示<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.annoyances.org/exec/forum/winxp/t1094485009 |title=Free space pie chart missing? |author=JCMIT |date=2004-09-06 |work=Annoyances.org |accessdate=2012-12-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050126211909/http://www.annoyances.org/exec/forum/winxp/t1094485009 |archivedate=2005-01-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。
* 在地址栏浏览文件路径地址<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.annoyances.org/exec/forum/winxp/t1104332485 |title='Disk Free Space' not displayed in Windows Explorer UNLESS viewing files under Desktop > My Computer > C: |author=aeneas kaolin |date=2004-12-29 |work=Annoyances.org |accessdate=2012-12-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050106062702/http://annoyances.org/exec/forum/winxp/t1104332485 |archivedate=2005-01-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、可移动驱动器<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newsgroups.derkeiler.com/Archive/Alt/alt.os.windows-xp/2006-06/msg00442.html|title=Free space no listed in status bar for removable drives|author=ranvel|date=2006-06-11|work=derkeiler.com|accessdate=2013-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407093151/http://newsgroups.derkeiler.com/Archive/Alt/alt.os.windows-xp/2006-06/msg00442.html|archive-date=2014-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、在资源管理器打开网络共享导航窗格（或文件夹）时，底部状态栏不再显示文件所在磁盘的剩余空间，仅显示驱动器路径的剩余空间。这与前文提到的被删除的拼图相结合，意味着不可在剩下的三个驱动器中即时查看剩余空间。
* [[命令提示符|命令提示符]]中，快速编辑模式和插入模式默认禁用，仅能重新启动每个窗口的标题<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/282301|title=Command Prompt QuickEdit Mode Is Disabled by Default in Windows XP|author=Microsoft|date=2006-01-15|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2013-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071216132559/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/282301|archive-date=2007-12-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* 目录图标从[[网络邻居|网络邻居]]移除<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/329495|title=The Directory icon in Entire Network in My Network Places is missing|author=Microsoft|date=2005-03-15|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070629142610/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/329495|archive-date=2007-06-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* Windows资源管理器的默认排序顺序改变，可通过编辑注册表恢复<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/319827|title=The sort order for files and folders whose names contain numerals is different in Windows Vista, Windows XP, and Windows Server 2003 than it is in Windows 2000|author=Microsoft|date=2007-08-28|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071117045047/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/319827|archive-date=2007-11-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* '''联系电话拨号器'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/285920|title=Phone Dialer Is Not Available in the Communications Menu|author=Microsoft|date=2006-01-15|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2013-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070312222148/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/285920|archive-date=2007-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>和{{link-en|网络会议|NetMeeting}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/298327|title=NetMeeting Is Not Available on the Windows XP "Communications" Menu|author=Microsoft|date=2007-05-07|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2013-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061208214314/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/298327|archive-date=2006-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>从[[开始菜单|开始菜单]]移除。

== 个性化设置 ==
* Windows 2000中的桌面主题工具，即{{link-en|Microsoft Plus!98|Microsoft Plus!98}}和后来被2000引入的用以选择应用主题和预览主题的主题工具中“每月主题更换”选项被移除，在XP中成为“显示”属性中“主题”选项卡。
* “显示”属性中“外观”选项卡不可保存或删除方案。
* “显示”属性中选择“背景”（2000）/桌面（XP）图案模式选项卡被删除。
* 三维迷宫（可能由于Windows徽标改变）和三维管道屏保被删除，三维管道中茶壶复活节彩蛋不适用于XP。

== 合併應用程式 ==
* Windows 98附加程序及2000程序——豪华版“[[CD播放程式|CD播放程式]]”被删除<ref name="kb284971">{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/284971|title=Unable to Locate Either CD Deluxe or CD Player Playlists in Windows Media Player|author=Microsoft|date=2007-01-29|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407081910/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/284971|archive-date=2014-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。取而代之的[[Windows_Media_Player|Windows Media Player]]中不含原有的上传音轨信息<ref>{{cite web|url=http://winsupersite.com/article/windows-95/plus-for-windows-98-reviewed-127376|title=Plus! for Windows 98 Review|author=Paul Thurrott|date=1998-06-25|work=Paul Thurrott's SuperSite for Windows|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130914230822/http://winsupersite.com/article/windows-95/plus-for-windows-98-reviewed-127376|archive-date=2013-09-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、点播下载音轨信息、音轨预览等功能。
* [[DVD播放器|DVD播放器]]简化成Windows Media Player的[[桩_(计算机)|桩]]。
* [[Imaging_for_Windows|Imaging for Windows]]被“图片和传真查看器”和“扫描仪和相机向导”取代<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/308979|title=Kodak imaging for Windows is not included with Windows XP|author=Microsoft|date=2007-03-22|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071016061201/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/308979|archive-date=2007-10-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但这两个程序不包括映像的高级功能<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ilixis.com/developer/kodak_history.html |title=Kodak/Wang Image OCX Controls - Some History |author=Ilixis Solutions |accessdate=2012-11-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229031646/http://www.ilixis.com/developer/kodak_history.html |archivedate=2012-02-29 }}</ref>。

== 协议 ==
* [[动态数据交换|NetDDE]]和[[NetBIOS|NetBIOS]]不再在默认情况下安装，但可透过Windows XP [[CD-ROM|CD-ROM]]安装<ref name="ee449431">{{cite web|url=http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ee449431.aspx|title=Understanding Application Compatibility|author=Microsoft|work=Microsoft TechNet|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120528045343/http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ee449431.aspx|archive-date=2012-05-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/301041|title=How to install NetBEUI on Windows XP|author=Microsoft|date=2005-06-23|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050913162658/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/301041|archive-date=2005-09-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* {{link-en|数据链路控制|Data Link Control}}[[网络协议|网络协议]]不再包括在系统内，但[[微软|微软]]提供协议下载<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/306037|title=The DLC Protocol Is Not Available in Windows XP|author=Microsoft|date=2002-10-11|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050409045044/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/306037|archive-date=2005-04-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* [[AppleTalk|可路由协议组]]不再包括<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/305989|title=The AppleTalk Protocol Is Not Available in Windows XP|author=Microsoft|date=2001-10-18|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050409044803/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/305989|archive-date=2005-04-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 子系统 ==
