== 硬件支持 ==
* 不再支持[[调制解调器|调制解调器]]、[[网卡|网卡]]及低于28.8Kbps的调制解调器原生支持等非[[即插即用|即插即用]]网络设备<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/295745|title=Non-Plug and Play Network Device Support in Windows XP|author=Microsoft|date=2007-12-01|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20041030215121/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/295745|archive-date=2004-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 大量{{link-en|SCSI主机适配器|SCSI host adapters}}不再支持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/270650|title=SCSI Host Adapters Removed from Windows XP|author=Microsoft|date=2006-01-27|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070713193006/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/270650|archive-date=2007-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* XP降低对[[NEC|NEC]][[PC-98|PC-98]]<ref name="gg463468" />和[[硅谷图形公司|硅谷图形公司]]320型和540型{{link-en|图形工作站|SGI Visual Workstation}}的支持<ref name="ee449431" />。

== 后续版本 ==
=== Service Pack 2 ===
* [[原始套接字|原始套接字]]支持大多被移除<ref>{{cite web|url=http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/desktop/ms740548.aspx|title=TCP/IP Raw Sockets (Windows)|author=Microsoft|date=2012-10-16|work=Microsoft Developer Network|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130128183317/http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/desktop/ms740548.aspx|archive-date=2013-01-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* {{link-en|TCP半开链接|TCP half-open}}数量受限<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.microsoft.com/products/ee/transform.aspx?ProdName=Windows+Operating+System&EvtID=4226&EvtSrc=Tcpip|title=Source: Tcpip ID: 4226 (Windows Operating System ) - Events And Errors Message Center: Message Details|author=Microsoft|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140529043926/http://www.microsoft.com/products/ee/transform.aspx?ProdName=Windows%2BOperating%2BSystem&EvtID=4226&EvtSrc=Tcpip|archive-date=2014-05-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* [[程序管理器|程序管理器]]变成根。
* [[Internet_Explorer_6|Internet Explorer 6]]捆绑版本中的媒体栏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/303130|title=The Radio Toolbar Is Unavailable in Internet Explorer 6|author=Microsoft|date=2007-01-31|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080309210019/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/303130|archive-date=2008-03-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>被电台工具栏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms533100.aspx|title=Media Bar|author=Microsoft|work=Microsoft Developer Network|accessdate=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211160218/https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms533100.aspx|archive-date=2017-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>取代，不再出现在打包版本的IE6中。
* [[Outlook_Express|Outlook Express]]捆绑版本移除了[[后台进程|后台]][[电子邮件|信息]][[压缩|压缩]]特性<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.insideoe.com/files/maintain.htm|title=Inside Outlook Express - Files and Setttings - Maintenance Part I|author=Tom Koch|date=2006-04-29|work=Inside Outlook Express|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101111328/http://www.insideoe.com/files/maintain.htm|archive-date=2012-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，禁用该特性，每压缩消息一百次，该程序将不被运行。

=== Service Pack 3 ===
*[[任务栏|任务栏]]中的“地址”工具栏因法律原因被微软移除<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/951448|title=The Address toolbar no longer appears on the taskbar after you install Windows XP Service Pack 3|author=Microsoft|date=2008-05-06|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080513075458/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/951448|archive-date=2008-05-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>，取代其的功能“[[Windows搜索|Windows桌面搜索]]”遭鼓吹。
*Internet Explorer桌面图标的特殊显示设置被移除<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tipandtrick.net/restore-missing-or-disappeared-ie-internet-explorer-desktop-icon-in-windows-xp-sp3/|title=Restore Missing or Disappeared IE (Internet Explorer) Desktop Icon in Windows XP SP3|date=2008-05-11|work=Tip and Trick|accessdate=2013-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130112070630/http://www.tipandtrick.net/restore-missing-or-disappeared-ie-internet-explorer-desktop-icon-in-windows-xp-sp3/|archive-date=2013-01-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*Service Pack 3不累积以前安装的[[服務包|服務包]]的内容，至少需要先安装SP1，SP2则包含在{{link-en|媒体中心Windows XP版|Windows XP Media Center Edition}}和2003版中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/cc507836.aspx|title=Installing Windows XP Service Pack 3 (SP3)|author=Microsoft|work=Microsoft TechNet|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105204312/http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/cc507836.aspx|archive-date=2012-11-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/949388|title=Windows XP Service Pack 3 installation fails with an error message, and the following error is logged in the service pack installation log: "8007F0F4 - STATUS_PREREQUISITE_FAILED"|author=Microsoft|date=2012-06-12|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120618022213/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/949388|archive-date=2012-06-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。微软证实可以进行尾流累积<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/950722|title=After you create Windows XP Service Pack 3 slipstreamed media, your product key is not accepted|author=Microsoft|date=2010-01-18|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2013-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100127064648/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/950722|archive-date=2010-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Media Center Edition 2005 ===
* 尽管用于[[Windows_XP版本列表|Windows XP专业版]]的媒体中心2005版正在开发中，但其域名支持不可用。微软表示这是需要用户快速切换到{{link-en|Windows媒体中心扩展器|Windows Media Center Extenders}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/887212|title=You cannot join your computer to a domain in Windows XP Media Center Edition 2005|author=Microsoft|date=2011-09-23|work=Microsoft Support|accessdate=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051101091747/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/887212|archive-date=2005-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在安装或升级前就已使用该功能的情况下例外，但这之后的域名支持被禁用。
* [[Windows_Media_Player|Windows Media Player]]6.4不包含在内。

